org.apache.hadoop.fs.http.server

Class FSOperations.StatusPair

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.fs.http.server.FSOperations.StatusPair
  • Enclosing class:
    FSOperations

    private static class FSOperations.StatusPair
extends Object
    This class is used to group a FileStatus and an AclStatus together. It's needed for the GETFILESTATUS and LISTSTATUS calls, which take most info from the FileStatus and a wee bit from the AclStatus.
